{"tid":1793614,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，依家d食客都痴撚線架","createTime":"2019-12-22T13:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T14:37:08.000Z","uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"509527a24848bfe059cda3e70077add448a27dde","tid":1793614,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:46:57.000Z","msg":"唉，話說小弟我讀書不成，中學畢業就局住要出來做野了，唯有跟隨住父母既步伐進入依個餐飲行業，一開始由細位做起，一路慢慢咁捱，終於係今年promote左做經理了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要一升經理就in charge個冬至period，準備定衝業績等攞年底個年終<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點撚知我仆你個街，係臨收工最尾1 round既時候，無啦啦有張枱勁撚嘈，咁我就行過去睇下搞乜啦，越行近越黎越嘈，仲見到有d其他枱既食客行過去嘈緊果張枱，個場面勁撚嘈，各種粗口飛黎飛去，又話乜野良心啊，暴力啊，洗腦啊....<br />\n<br />\n我心裡邊暗屌左一聲之後，收拾好心情，準備上去調停啦...<br />\n<br />\n轟！一聲，跟住張枱係我眼前反撚左，然後有個後生仔頭也不回走左，我當堂呆曬，你老母我做左20幾年野都係第一次係電影以外見到反枱，張枱反完仲好似個屎忽咁裂開左，仲有成碟菜飛撚左落我條褲度，我當下係完全唔知到點做，就連廚房大佬都出左黎睇戲...<br />\n<br />\n隔左5mins後，我終於從震撼中回過頭並且靈機一觸，即刻換上笑容行過去個廢佬度問句：洗唔洗上埋個生果盤啊？ 驚佢撞聾我仲特登大聲d問tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢就話唔要啦...<br />\n<br />\n跟住隔離枱有個傻仔跌左隻雞髀係地好似個怨婦咁鵝住曬，我唯有靈機一觸，將啱先隔離枱碟生果盤送比佢地當補償啦...我真係dllm，依家d食客都痴撚線既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，有無人知邊隻膠水可以痴返張枱，同埋邊度有得買，唔想比人扣無左個年終啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346fa24c1ba9e8bc8cbae0bfeeb39b3562952907","tid":1793614,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"求救啊連登仔們<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f490818add787cea47e0d10cda1fd2533ea5cb","tid":1793614,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffb5ef99f128c10a9141fefe92b5fcbb80b928c","tid":1793614,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b47e828a1832fba9fbaac5ecbc1c19afb004e72","tid":1793614,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾post 拉"},{"pid":"fd69fe2bffd56b9b921cfc563503a19940fd44ba","tid":1793614,"uid":126649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"唔明你想點撚樣"},{"pid":"1e255574d938697512f2d0b4ab902b4411a89478","tid":1793614,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦ON9仔<br />\n你覺得自己好幽默"},{"pid":"22ca834da7de21f0a9ffab9ec370272194ba958c","tid":1793614,"uid":17362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人食冬至飯食撚到反尻埋張枱！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39f49faf7121a3a442441c5a35f1b5ed6fa62304","tid":1793614,"uid":17362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"食冬至飯見到隔離反枱，仲爭啲打架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dd1dbbbf8f973fd598fee528c7b610913e4b701","tid":1793614,"uid":17362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"有冇廚房佬version<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dcc9b54229a81750199ec0e87a2cfa4b6cb110","tid":1793614,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike"